title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 6 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 6 2022
description:
Children exposed to graphic sexuality during disturbing Dallas pride parade. Videos of children at a drag strip show. Biden's Commerce Secretary Gina Raimondo celebrates administration's response to baby formula shortage. Arizona Attorney General Mark Brnovich joins C&B to talk about the "largest invasion of the southern border since the Alamo," the Biden administration's failure of securing the border and of rising gas prices destroying the middle class. Ron DeSantis continues to lead the charge against the left.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
